{'en': {'shortDesc': 'A podcast client and feed aggregator', 'pkgName': 'gpodder', 'longDesc': u'gPodder is a podcast receiver/catcher. You can subscribe to feeds ("podcasts") and automatically download new audio and video content. Downloaded content can be played on your computer or synchronized to iPods, MTP-based players, filesystem-based MP3 players and Bluetooth enabled mobile phones. YouTube video feeds are also supported.\n\nThis package provides the "gpodder" GUI and the "gpo" CLI utility.'}}